  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To study whether the combination of ultrasound guidance and stimulating catheter could reduce
      the time for needle and catheter insertion compared with using stimulating catheter alone.
      Secondary outcomes: analgesic effects after the surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
